lkm (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Merges lkf (Linux Kernel Framework) and ukm (Universal Kernel Manager).
  * Supports apt, pacman, dnf, zypper, apk, portage, xbps, and nix backends.
  * Adds xbps backend for Void Linux.
  * Adds nix backend for NixOS with configuration.nix patching.
  * GUI Build tab for lkf profile and custom kernel builds.

 -- lkm contributors <lkm@example.com>  Sun, 30 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000
